{"tid":2386952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(RTHK)聶德權：公務員擁有國籍安排不應與BNO問題混為一談","createTime":"2021-01-30T02:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T03:15:17.000Z","uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"77a02285c807bca267f17355cab13cf6a5775fe1","tid":2386952,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:55:18.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局局長聶德權出席一個電台節目後被問到，公務員是否要放棄持有英國國民(海外)護照BNO，他回應時說，外交部已就BNO問題發出清晰訊息，特區政府亦已表示，BNO不再作為旅遊證件及身份證明。<br />\n<br />\n至於公務員擁有國籍的安排，是根據《基本法》及香港法例現有規定進行，不應將兩件事混為一談。<br />\n<br />\n政府要求現職公務員在4星期內簽署聲明，擁護《基本法》和效忠特區，聶德權在一個電台節目說，現時已將所有相關文件發送予現職同事，他們要在二月底交回聲明，部門會先整理，再由局方跟進。對於國家主席習近平早前聽取行政長官林鄭月娥述職時提及有關「愛國者治港」的言論，聶德權認為愛國者即是要擁護《基本法》，接受香港憲制秩序、香港作為中國一部分、落實好一國兩制，公務員隊伍為政治體制一部分，當然有同樣要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de75a88d028020a9b56d068393b2a0e60139b97","tid":2386952,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"效忠完有 BNO 咪抄家囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中共無錢唯有吸大家水<br />\n<br />\n大和：若香港走資不超過1.2萬億元 任何壓力可控<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592390337608&amp;issue=20200617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1592390337608%26issue%3D20200617&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=243b51da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592390337608&amp;issue=20200617</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">原來11月走左 10000 億，走多 2000 億佢就收皮！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"daef4c7c2ecc26f8a09e2761afa5cd34ba2f2402","tid":2386952,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百<span class=\"red\"></span>國聯軍。<br />\n</span><br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"84aaac032257ec0131620c411932ee60b3214874","tid":2386952,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:56:57.000Z","msg":"至於公務員擁有國籍的安排，是根據《基本法》及香港法例現有規定進行，不應將兩件事混為一談。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66585dd50e4c086ef78589a540c25e2f2a75ad8e","tid":2386952,"uid":99397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"自己有利就基本法，無利就歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44daf61952db1eb5d3eb08cb42f96a16412bea33","tid":2386952,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77a02285c807bca267f17355cab13cf6a5775fe1","ti